  "title": "CLINIC ASSISTANT / JUNIOR TRANSLATOR (BAHASA INDONESIA)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Assist in translation for patients / clinic staff.</li><li>Assist in clinic’s day-to-day operations and functions.</li><li>Assist the Clinic Manager and Medical Director in the assigned clinic.</li><li>Responsible for all aspects of customer service including but not limited to cashiering, appointment booking, and answering customer enquiries.</li><li>Responsible for all matters pertaining to insurance, Medisave, and Letter of Guarantee(s).</li><li>Liaise with customers, vendors, suppliers, and local regulatory bodies when required.</li><li>Assist in the renewal of relevant licenses.</li><li>Other duties assigned by the Clinic Manager and/or Medical Director as required.</li></ul>",
